  title="Contact Us - Get in Touch | MedCare Solutions"
  description="Contact MedCare Solutions for professional healthcare services. Reach our team at (555) 123-4567 or visit us at 123 Healthcare Drive, Springfield, IL. Monday-Saturday service."
>
